{"word":"ὑπερβάλλω","slug":"ὑπερβάλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπερβάλλω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπέρ\">ὑπέρ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάλλω\">βάλλω</a></el>] ‘proceed beyond a limiting point or degree’, <b>surpass <a href='B:540 3:10'>2 Cor 3:10</a>; <a href='B:540 9:14'>9:14</a>; <a href='B:560 1:19'>Eph 1:19</a>; <a href='B:560 2:7'>2:7</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> of comparison <el>ὑπερβάλλουσα τῆς γνώσεως <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀγάπη\">ἀγάπη</a></el> a love surpassing comprehension <b><a href='B:560 3:19'>Eph 3:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπερβαλλόντως\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπερβολή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}